  "title": "90.1",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The trail leads over a small rise and you find yourself looking down\ninto a clearing. In the center, maybe fifty meters away, you can see a\nreclaimer. Strangely, it\u2019s standing perfectly still."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Then you see something moving alongside it. What you thought was\na large flowering weed appears to be some sort of being. As you\nwatch, it runs an appendage lightly along the reclaimer\u2019s back, and\nyou see small white flowers sprout from its spine."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You take a single step, and even that slight movement causes the\nbeing\u2019s head to turn in your direction. You\u2019re going to have to\napproach very cautiously if you don\u2019t want to scare it off."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "em",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Clear the Verdessian with"
                },
                {
                  "type": "span",
                  "items": [
                    {
                      "type": "icon",
                      "icon": "progress",
                      "color": "black"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "to silently observe its behavior."
                }
              ],
              "color": "blue"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
